      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape, having been well-loved and looked after. It runs super smoothly and is just waiting for someone to take it on its next big adventure! It's the perfect dependable choice if you're looking for quality without the 'brand-new' price tag. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'd love to chat!",
