    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333 hp through its high-revving individual throttle bodies. Mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission, the chassis dynamics are sharpened by a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high torque loads. The suspension remains communicative with refreshed bushings and dampers. The interior shows a light, honest patina, reflecting a mechanically sorted machine that has been driven as intended and meticulously serviced.",
