      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape, perfect for everything from grocery runs to road trips! I've made sure to keep up with the maintenance, so it runs like a dream and looks great too. It's ready and waiting for its next adventure\u2014come see it for yourself, I'm sure you'll love it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
