    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its independent throttle bodies and high-revving atmospheric performance. This unit is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed to ensure longevity, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate common E46 chassis fatigue, maintaining factory-spec torsional rigidity. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings for precise turn-in, and the braking system remains fade-resistant with recent fluid service. While the paintwork and interior show honest wear consistent with a well-enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical vitals are in excellent health, offering a visceral and communicative driving experience.",
